org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus.impl

Class ModbusMasterImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus.impl.ModbusMasterImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModbusMaster

    public class ModbusMasterImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements ModbusMaster
    An implementation of the model object 'Master'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Slaves
    • Endpoint
    • Id
    • Protocol Type
    • Inter Frame Delay
